{"tid":897194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[雙11] 今日係美國嘅退伍軍人節","createTime":"2018-11-10T16:36:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T01:57:16.000Z","uid":51620,"like":54,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"f64d32c957bcbd0308ad8b1ef23312d2ca3a639e","tid":897194,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T16:36:18.000Z","msg":"老兵節，退伍軍人節或退伍軍人紀念日（Veterans Day）是美國聯邦假日，定於11月11日。這是美國比較重要的一個全國性節日，人們藉此向退伍軍人、特別是參加過歷次戰爭的退伍軍人表達敬意。<br />\n<br />\n11月11日在英國以及加拿大等大英國協國家也是一個紀念日。這一天被稱為「Remembrance Day」，中文有時被翻譯為「國殤紀念日」或「悼念日」。法國和比利時也在這一天紀念「休戰日」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/12/United_States_Department_of_Veterans_Affairs_Veterans_Day_2009_poster.jpg/800px-United_States_Department_of_Veterans_Affairs_Veterans_Day_2009_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F1%2F12%2FUnited_States_Department_of_Veterans_Affairs_Veterans_Day_2009_poster.jpg%2F800px-United_States_Department_of_Veterans_Affairs_Veterans_Day_2009_poster.jpg&h=adc8006d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%80%81%E5%85%B5%E8%8A%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%2585%25B5%25E8%258A%2582&d=INALvyyzIH9cpXQf1t%2F%2BEsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=36e74ee8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%80%81%E5%85%B5%E8%8A%82</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"104f2d3188631c69b0b5e9996f880d65c2faa391","tid":897194,"uid":51620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T16:38:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M1wLtAXDgqg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DM1wLtAXDgqg&d=INALvyyzIH9cpXQf1t%2F%2BEsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=dc5ad385\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M1wLtAXDgqg</a>"},{"pid":"1f82b42a466febd